<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>StudyMatch - Find Your Perfect Study Partner</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #ffffff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .header-container {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        header {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 16px 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 21px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.022em;
        }

        header nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        header nav a {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            border-radius: 980px;
            transition: all 150ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            background: #f5f5f7;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            padding: 140px 24px 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f7 0%, #ffffff 50%, #f5f5f7 100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 72px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.003em;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 1.381;
            color: #6e6e73;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .features {
            padding: 120px 24px;
            background: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
        }

        .features-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .features-header h2 {
            font-size: 56px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.003em;
        }

        .features-header p {
            font-size: 21px;
            color: #6e6e73;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 48px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0071e3 0%, #0051d5 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 113, 227, 0.3);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.003em;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: #6e6e73;
            line-height: 1.47059;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .about-section {
            padding: 120px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f5f5f7;
        }

        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.003em;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 21px;
            line-height: 1.381;
            color: #6e6e73;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 64px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        footer p {
            color: #86868b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 120px 24px 80px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 48px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 19px;
            }

            .features {
                padding: 80px 24px;
            }

            .features-header h2 {
                font-size: 40px;
            }

            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 32px;
            }

            .feature-card {
                padding: 32px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header-container">
        <header>
            <a href="/" class="logo">StudyMatch</a>
            <nav>
                <% if (userLoggedIn) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login">Sign In</a>
                    <a href="/register">Get Started</a>
                <% } %>
            </nav>
        </header>
    </div>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Find Your Perfect<br>Study Partner</h1>
                <p>Connect with students who share your courses, schedule, and learning style. Build productive study groups and achieve academic success together.</p>
                <% if (!userLoggedIn) { %>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-large">Get Started</a>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">Sign In</a>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-large">Go to Dashboard</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="features-header">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>Simple steps to find your ideal study partner</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                    <div class="feature-icon">1</div>
                    <h3>Set Your Preferences</h3>
                    <p>Tell us about your courses, availability, and preferred study style to get personalized matches.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <div class="feature-icon">2</div>
                    <h3>Find Matches</h3>
                    <p>We'll match you with students who have similar study preferences and compatible schedules.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="feature-icon">3</div>
                    <h3>Start Studying</h3>
                    <p>Connect with your matches and start productive study sessions together.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>About StudyMatch</h2>
            <p>StudyMatch is a student-focused platform designed to help university students find compatible study partners and small study groups.</p>
            <p>We match users based on factors like courses, availability, study habits, and goals, making it easier to connect with people who study in similar ways.</p>
            <p>The goal is to improve academic performance, accountability, and well-being by turning studying from an isolated task into a collaborative, supportive experience.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 StudyMatch. Created by a UofT student.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
